{"tid":1295583,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊有內鬼！","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:06:44.000Z","uid":259980,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c860df6bc8da17d19e2fca8d00ed85ae1324c608","tid":1295583,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xrg7jag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrg7jag.jpg&h=912cdb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反黃屍專頁幫手宣傳下<br />\n前線指揮官中懷疑有黃屍內鬼<br />\n故意違抗一哥命令<br />\n叫前線警員撞推、挑釁記者<br />\n又打一般市民<br />\n嚴重損害警隊聲譽<br />\n重申警隊絕對重視新聞自由<br />\n要求革職當命指揮官<br />\n還警隊一個清白"},{"pid":"fe7042e8614d1b1534da3cac3639a2694c838986","tid":1295583,"uid":268327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4X6zGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4X6zGM.png&h=a721d437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似蟲蟲特工隊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蟲蟲特攻隊 - 香港人Version<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295142</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8f59136cfec92216dbb709da0b24a9c48467f9","tid":1295583,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"其實佢冇講錯呀，係佢對記者客氣姐<br />\n佢d下屬佢管唔到嘛"},{"pid":"763a18be531bd238abcb4e608ce3d5a6c6ae54c6","tid":1295583,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫手推上熱門<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［重要］區議會選舉招募各路人馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295057</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，光復行動冇可能每日都做<br />\n好似屯門公園搞到今日咁烏煙瘴氣區議員責無旁貸<br />\n要清洗屯門公園始終要由根源做起<br />\n所以除左投立法會外<br />\n都請記得投票區議會踢走自動當選建制派<br />\n<br />\n唔好再俾建制派霸哂啲議席<br />\n就算唔係參選都可以做提名人，義工，助選團<br />\n行出第一步拒絕自動當選！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總台TG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDistrictCouncil2019&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=ccdd4b97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019</a><br />\n</span></span><br />\n登記左做選民既全部入group<br />\n急需大量提名人，義工助選團，Design等職位<br />\n入group後右下角Discuss入公頻搵各區admin<br />\n<br />\n要對抗黑警濫權一定要有議員抗衡<br />\n否則只會一直任人魚肉"},{"pid":"47bf4249b906f697f932d9df7eae855da79e3887","tid":1295583,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"48fb14742b40dae261351ef4289554311edf35d7","tid":1295583,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:33:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5bc171aab8b57409f9bc48a6eb511f94b1919732","tid":1295583,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<code>我無野講 (不斷講&nbsp; 問咩都係依句)\n唔簽任何文件\n叫律師\n同自己講唔好驚 當人廢up\n唔解電話鎖</code>"},{"pid":"8df7740865cf7b9a3a145fb7b6ca366898d3bff3","tid":1295583,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:06:44.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}